      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Aug 31 article on Adam Roberts, a Long Island man who pleaded guilty to killing his parents than setting fire to their vacation house</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Thursday about Adam Roberts, a Long Island man who pleaded guilty to having killed his parents and then having set fire to their vacation home, included an erroneous date from the district attorney for the murders. They occurred on Nov. 13, 1999, not Nov. 14.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article on Thursday about Adam Roberts, a Long Island man who pleaded guilty to having killed his parents and then having set fire to their vacation home, included an erroneous date from the district attorney for the murders. They occurred on Nov. 13, 1999, not Nov. 14.</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
